You may want to look at Izzet Coskun's
<a href="http://homepages.math.uic.edu/~coskun/bagslist.pdf">list</a>
(with lots of references)
or Johan de Jong's
<a href="http://www.math.columbia.edu/~dejong/seminar/list_papers.html">
seminar page</a>
for more topics.
